    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个围绕青蛙弹跳战术来进行“蛙快打”对战的故事。你要通过收集、购买、交换各式各样的小青蛙来打造一支超级无敌厉害的蛙阵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/6b0dd9da176e097ba249e6020aef646d.poster.avif?t=1771865187\" width=800 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/6b0dd9da176e097ba249e6020aef646d.webm?t=1771865187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/6b0dd9da176e097ba249e6020aef646d.mp4?t=1771865187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上击败地方恶霸的征程，却总被意外带偏节奏 —— 演奏音乐、潜入蜂巢（伪装成蜜蜂），说不定还会和吸血鬼来场雪橇竞速赛哦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/f0138e34df5388670fd53b884bce0e41.poster.avif?t=1771865187\" width=800 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/f0138e34df5388670fd53b884bce0e41.webm?t=1771865187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/f0138e34df5388670fd53b884bce0e41.mp4?t=1771865187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏全程由我们和朋友们亲自献声配音，更有一众意想不到的神秘嘉宾惊喜献嗓。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/9feb4bd96d84dbea3db979b974c22608.poster.avif?t=1771865187\" width=800 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/9feb4bd96d84dbea3db979b974c22608.webm?t=1771865187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/9feb4bd96d84dbea3db979b974c22608.mp4?t=1771865187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背上你的蛤包，数清楚那些可可嘟，踏入这个温柔又无厘头的世界——在这里，所有矛盾都得靠“蛙快打”来解决！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/089b57fa0a83fc22f4fe10971f0dc260.poster.avif?t=1771865187\" width=800 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/089b57fa0a83fc22f4fe10971f0dc260.webm?t=1771865187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051010/extras/089b57fa0a83fc22f4fe10971f0dc260.mp4?t=1771865187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>游戏特色</strong></u></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一只穿着青蛙连体衣的熊</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位巨大的骷髅</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位正常大小的骷髅</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至少12段讲述社区与自我认同“蛙心蛙肺”的感人情节</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还有，可以给青蛙戴帽子！:3</p></li></ul>",
